snippet.title: Alien Marauder - Early Access Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Alien Marauder on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1516750/Alien_Marauder

Alien Marauder is a real-time strategy game with survival and confrontation theme. In this game, you will be the leader to a treacherous alien planet, build and defend base to survive against the vaxan waves. Make the right decision!

Source: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QkSiyrspEAc

#AlienMarauder #trailer #gametrailers #games #gaming
